sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Payment API
    participant Idem as Idempotency Cache
    participant Orch as Saga Orchestrator
    participant PSP as External PSP
    participant Ledger as Ledger (event-sourced)

    Note over C,Ledger: CHARGE FLOW (Saga with idempotency)
    C->>API: POST /charge (idempotency-key, body)
    API->>Idem: lookup key
    alt key exists, same body
        Idem-->>API: cached response
        API-->>C: 200 prior result
    else key exists, different body
        Idem-->>API: conflict
        API-->>C: 422 programming error
    else new key
        API->>Idem: write key=in_progress
        Idem-->>API: ok
        API->>Orch: start Saga (charge_id)

        Note over Orch,Ledger: STEP 1 — Risk check
        Orch->>Orch: reserve risk score
        alt risk fails
            Orch-X API: blocked
            API->>Idem: store fail response
            API-->>C: 402 declined
        end

        Note over Orch,Ledger: STEP 2 — Authorize via PSP
        Orch->>PSP: authorize (idempotency-key)
        alt PSP timeout / unknown
            PSP--xOrch: timeout
            Orch->>Orch: mark requires_verification
            Note over Orch,PSP: reconcile via PSP GET-by-key
        else PSP declines
            PSP-->>Orch: declined
            Orch->>Orch: release risk reservation
            Orch-->>API: failed
            API-->>C: 402 declined
        else PSP authorizes
            PSP-->>Orch: auth_token, psp_charge_id
        end

        Note over Orch,Ledger: STEP 3 — Ledger debit/credit
        Orch->>Ledger: append debit user_card + credit merchant_payable
        alt ledger fails
            Ledger--xOrch: error
            Orch->>PSP: void auth (compensation)
            PSP-->>Orch: voided
            Orch-->>API: failed
            API-->>C: 500 retryable
        else ledger ok
            Ledger-->>Orch: entries committed
        end

        Note over Orch,Ledger: STEP 4 — Capture
        Orch->>PSP: capture
        alt capture fails
            PSP--xOrch: error
            Orch->>Ledger: reverse entries (compensation)
            Ledger-->>Orch: reversed
            Orch-->>API: failed
            API-->>C: 500
        else capture ok
            PSP-->>Orch: captured
            Orch->>Ledger: append capture transfer entries
            Ledger-->>Orch: ok
        end

        Orch-->>API: succeeded
        API->>Idem: store final response
        API-->>C: 200 {charge_id, succeeded}
    end

    Note over PSP,Ledger: ASYNC — daily reconciliation diffs ledger vs PSP settlement
